; Pure MongoDB query/update semantics over Bson: selector matching, update modifiers, projection,
; sort, document diffing (+ LCS for ordered observe), and id generation. Used by Minimongo and
; (later) the native Live engine; bundled into the npm artifact. Dependency-free beyond Bson, so it
; cross-compiles to JavaScript. Inline tests live in ../test (this library stays dep-free).
(library
 (name query)
 (public_name fennec-mongo.query)
 (libraries bson))
